'''Radyo ng Bayan''' (DXRP 675 kHz [[Davao City]]) is an [[AM broadcasting|AM]] station owned and operated by [[Philippine Broadcasting Service]] in the [[Philippines]]. Located at Braveheart Bldg., Matina, [[Davao City]].
